Super Sector is a very exciting game on android platform.I like it very much.
But the game always crashed when I got high in my Samsung Galaxy S4. 
For this reason I decided to implement this game on iOS platform using cocos2d-x.

超级六边形是安卓平台下面一款非常刺激的游戏。我非常喜欢它。
但是在我的三星galaxy s4上面，它经常在我玩地正high的时候崩溃。
由于这个原因我决定ios平台下面自己实现一个，使用cocos2d-x框架。
